      Subinterfaces of WTable.TableModel in com.github.bordertech.wcomponents

      static interface  WTable.BeanBoundTableModel

      class  AbstractTableModel
      A skeleton implementation of a simple data model that does not support sorting, selectability, expandability or editability.
      class  AdapterBasicTableModel
      Adapter to allow classes that implement the AdapterBasicTableModel.BasicTableModel interface to be used as the model for WTable.
      class  EmptyTableModel
      An empty data model implementation, the default model used by WTable.
      class  SimpleBeanBoundTableModel
      A simple table data model that is bound to a list of beans.
